WEBVTT

00:05:28.560 --> 00:05:32.176
and they saw centuries
of rigid inequality.

00:05:32.200 --> 00:05:34.376
The king and the few elites around him

00:05:34.400 --> 00:05:37.256
had all the pleasures
and comforts of the world

00:05:37.280 --> 00:05:40.496
while the mass majority
suffered from backbreaking labor

00:05:40.520 --> 00:05:41.760
and harsh poverty.

00:05:42.720 --> 00:05:45.360
You don't need a history book
to see that this is true.

00:05:46.120 --> 00:05:48.336
The Khmer word for "I,"

00:05:48.360 --> 00:05:49.560
for "me,"

00:05:50.480 --> 00:05:51.840
is khnhom.

00:05:53.240 --> 00:05:56.936
This very same word can also mean "slave"

00:05:56.960 --> 00:06:00.696
and dancers were in fact known
as knhom preah robam,